description.narrative: UNICEF support to strengthen service delivery has continued in 2020. Key inputs include financial and technical assistance to strengthen the coordination and capacity of the child protection workforce comprising 34 Child Protection and Welfare Officers, 29,674 IZU (child protection volunteers), and the justice workforce. A pilot child friendly space was also established in one RIB station in Kigali to attend to child victims, witnesses or suspects. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:07/08/2020
